This is a placeholder file. Replace this with an actual 1200x630 PNG image for Open Graph social media previews.

To create your OG image:
1. Design a 1200x630px image with your name, title, and branding
2. Save it as og-image.png
3. Replace this file with your actual image

Recommended tools:
- Canva (free templates available)
- Figma
- Photoshop
- Online OG image generators
